str1="what we think we become;we are python programmers"
index=0
substring="we"
while index<len(str1):
    index=str1.find(substring,index)
    if index==-1:
        break
    print(substring, "found at",index)
    index=index+2
count=str1.count(substring)
print("The count is:",count)

we found at 5
we found at 14
we found at 24
The count is: 3

